description:
**All Star Freaks is a digital collectible card series of Freak All Star athletes and personalities.  All 1/1's.**  

500 numbered base cards in total + special insert cards.

$FREAKS

- Series 1 (Base cards #1-100) + Inserts
- Series 2 (Base cards #100-200) + Inserts
- Series 3 (Base cards #200-300) + Inserts
- Series 4 (Base cards #300-400) + Inserts
- Series 5 (Base cards #400-500) + Inserts

Follow along on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/AllStarFreaks)
Join the official Freaks [Discord](https://discord.gg/g5fWbJGPaK)

AllStarFreaks are 100% parody fan art pieces intended as humor/homage and have no affiliation with the NBA or players.  

$FREAKS
